This is the Bayes classifier for Gaussian pattern classes, extended from a part of the project 'Gait 
recognization using Kinect' on class Human Motion Analysis. Details of the function is in the .m file.

Reference: 'Digital Image Processing 3/e' by Rafael C. Gonzalez and Richard E. Woods.
